org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Interaction

Interface SwInteractionResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwResource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MessageComResource, NotificationResource, SharedDataComResource, SwCommunicationResource, SwMutualExclusionResource, SwSynchronizationResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MessageComResourceImpl, NotificationResourceImpl, SharedDataComResourceImpl, SwCommunicationResourceImpl, SwInteractionResourceImpl, SwMutualExclusionResourceImpl, SwSynchronizationResourceImpl

    public interface SwInteractionResource
extends SwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Sw Interaction Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Intra Memory Partition Interaction
    • Waiting Queue Policy
    • Waiting Queue Capacity
    • Waiting Policy Elements
    See Also:
    SW_InteractionPackage.getSwInteractionResource()
